{"tid":230623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［嫁錯郎］新婚夫妻赴斐濟度蜜月　新娘溺斃身亡","createTime":"2017-05-05T13:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T01:56:54.000Z","uid":41351,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc404eaa7a539a151f9a14915c618463041bb810","tid":230623,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"香港一對新婚夫妻赴斐濟度蜜月，沒想到新娘昨日卻在當地傳出溺斃身亡，新人從此天人永隔。<br />\n29歲陳姓女子和葉姓丈夫上月才在香港辦婚宴，本周初赴斐濟度蜜月。新娘母親表示，昨日親家突然上門告知女兒死訊，讓她頓時晴天霹靂無法接受。據悉，新娘昨天和丈夫在海邊游泳，丈夫先上岸整理相機準備拍照，沒多久發現妻子在水中載浮載沉，連忙將她救上岸，然後送院搶救，惜已不治。<br />\n斐濟為香港新婚夫婦度蜜月的勝地，四面環海，是遊客熱捧地點。根據當地機構統計，於2005年至2015年，斐濟共發生482起溺水意外，平均每年達50起。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170505/1112400/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170505%2F1112400%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6cc06633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170505/1112400/</a><br />\n明知老婆唔識游水就寸步不離啦<br />\n今次點賠返個女比人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/211229_e5fdd1d5a81bd7f266e20380699d0217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F211229_e5fdd1d5a81bd7f266e20380699d0217.jpg&h=81a2c367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/211230_e5fdd1d5a81bd7f266e20380699d0217.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F211230_e5fdd1d5a81bd7f266e20380699d0217.jpg&h=e5f44b24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88dac3dba3292de5b9a75bf752fb0d24042c05f5","tid":230623,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e880124dd8c2f0fa2b2cfae33c7b6b335d8beab","tid":230623,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起義不容情劇情"},{"pid":"d0b5fdabc7a19a25a1ce02d10b4bcb0d8863a8da","tid":230623,"uid":29609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫先上岸整理相機準備拍照，沒多久發現妻子在水中載浮載沉</span>"},{"pid":"688d3a24e6aed6e1c1d80c7041c79a18e814bf78","tid":230623,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"柯南"},{"pid":"58694ee58da9f9a526cf581dc244fad805cc72e2","tid":230623,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"10bf4838f8e60cb5ef517e6da9035d8ac65f5866","tid":230623,"uid":29609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70a1f0d49249973e500ade2be7d0ff4c3ddac49","tid":230623,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"擋災"},{"pid":"8347bef0a3fa88891e421659e0da7b27ee3244ac","tid":230623,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要積口德請排隊</blockquote><br />\n排定隊先<br />\n個女人係咪有錢人？"},{"pid":"335e0077ab6309c18c0cded21ff4447e3915f6c9","tid":230623,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"咁就無咗個老婆...陰公"},{"pid":"43df805a39ed237c2c7e3651ffd149b4e090b417","tid":230623,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"諗起我左眼見到鬼"},{"pid":"9f6e823227c2f2f382eb4c76bdbd7905f0e78171","tid":230623,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解諗起義不容情劇情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/234821_387885794c06f8c57f9cfaed472c9d90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F234821_387885794c06f8c57f9cfaed472c9d90.jpg&h=ac9a5505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禽獸康：對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65b246de3db7643cab3da965ffd9f9c4d4a705f","tid":230623,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔快諗籍口屌鳩死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議一： 死港女晒錢執斐濟，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議二：明知唔熟水性都落海抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議三：明知老婆唔識游水都唔睇緊抵撚死（多謝巴打提供）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎繼續創作"},{"pid":"2b894ea54457090cac4183e36e39ac7e14d7542e","tid":230623,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a10401217a5d3bd0de257198c7098f6d005609ab","tid":230623,"uid":48145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係自殺一係就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扮意外 可能事先買重保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知賠幾多呢 佢就fatfat la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除非好憎個老婆OR帽左 唔會為左幾百萬整死自己老婆掛 話晒都用咁多錢同心機溝加娶個老婆番嚟"}]}